## IBAN Validation Rules

### Slovak IBAN Format
- Country code: SK
- Check digits: 2 digits
- Bank code: 4 digits
- Account number: 10 digits
- Total length: 24 characters
- Example: SK3112000000198742637541

### Major Slovak Banks
- Slovenská sporiteľňa: 0900
- VÚB banka: 0200
- Tatra banka: 1100
- ČSOB: 7500
- UniCredit Bank: 1111
- mBank: 8360
